    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-Variable Differential Lock. Crucially, the chassis has been addressed with a rear subframe reinforcement kit and the rod bearings have been replaced\u2014essential preventative measures for this platform. The suspension geometry is maintained by refreshed bushings and a set of Bilstein dampers, ensuring the car retains its signature neutral handling and steering feedback. While the exterior exhibits minor stone chips and light patina consistent with a well-driven enthusiast vehicle, the drivetrain is in excellent synchronization, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience.",
